        public static final int[] ActionBar
        ============================================ Attributes used to style the Action Bar. These should be set on your theme; the default actionBarStyle will propagate them to the correct elements as needed. Please Note: when overriding attributes for an ActionBar style you must specify each attribute twice: once with the "android:" namespace prefix and once without.

        Includes the following attributes:

        AttributeDescription
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:background Specifies a background drawable for the action bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:backgroundSplit Specifies a background drawable for the bottom component of a split action bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:backgroundStacked Specifies a background drawable for a second stacked row of the action bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:contentInsetEnd Minimum inset for content views within a bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:contentInsetLeft Minimum inset for content views within a bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:contentInsetRight Minimum inset for content views within a bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:contentInsetStart Minimum inset for content views within a bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:customNavigationLayout Specifies a layout for custom navigation.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:displayOptions Options affecting how the action bar is displayed.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:divider Specifies the drawable used for item dividers.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:elevation Elevation for the action bar itself
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:height Specifies a fixed height.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:hideOnContentScroll Set true to hide the action bar on a vertical nested scroll of content.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:homeAsUpIndicator Up navigation glyph
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:homeLayout Specifies a layout to use for the "home" section of the action bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:icon Specifies the drawable used for the application icon.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:indeterminateProgressStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an indeterminate progress spinner.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:itemPadding Specifies padding that should be applied to the left and right sides of system-provided items in the bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:logo Specifies the drawable used for the application logo.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:navigationMode The type of navigation to use.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:popupTheme Reference to a theme that should be used to inflate popups shown by widgets in the action bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:progressBarPadding Specifies the horizontal padding on either end for an embedded progress bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:progressBarStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an embedded progress bar.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:subtitle Specifies subtitle text used for navigationMode="normal"
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:subtitleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for subtitle text.
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:title Specifies title text used for navigationMode="normal"
        com.SoftwareProject.beuth:titleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for title text.
